# Generated branding images (version number images)
# 
# Strategy for branding.png files:
# - Default files ARE committed to Git for local development use
# - During build process, build_assets generates new files with current version
# - Generated files are used in builds but NOT committed (via git_reset in fastlane)
# - This avoids frequent binary file commits while ensuring dev environment works
#
# Note: These files are NOT in .gitignore because they need to be in Git
# for local development. The fastlane 'all' lane uses git_reset to discard
# generated changes, preventing daily commits of version number images.
